-We're making port tonight.

1:04:05.232 --> 1:04:07.713
-Freya, if any of us
is infected, then --

1:04:07.713 --> 1:04:09.454
-Then we'll be better off
in hospital.

1:04:09.454 --> 1:04:13.110
-Freya, wait!
You know Christmas Island?

1:04:13.110 --> 1:04:15.112
-What?
-It has the world's

1:04:15.112 --> 1:04:18.289
