Just a few ants.

1:04:24.121 --> 1:04:26.210
Now there aren't
anymore red crabs.

1:04:26.210 --> 1:04:28.212
Do you see what I mean?

1:04:28.212 --> 1:04:31.345
-Yeah. The crabs should
have gone to hospital.

1:04:31.345 --> 1:04:33.782
-This is what I do.

1:04:33.782 --> 1:04:36.350
Faunal behavior in spe--
-Yes, in a lab.

1:04:36.350 --> 1:04:38.875
But this is the real world,
with real people!

1:04:38.875 --> 1:04:41.007
-And in the real world,
if we go ashore

1:04:41.007 --> 1:04:42.487
and one of us is a carrier,

1:04:42.487 --> 1:04:44.576
then those things will spread,
really fast.

1:04:44.576 --> 1:04:46.883
-Sudi is my responsibility.

1:04:46.883 --> 1:04:48.275
And he's bleeding
to death in there.

1:04:48.275 --> 1:04:50.712
-We can't just think about Sudi.

1:04:53.280 --> 1:04:56.762
I am not losing
one more crew member.

1:05:01.245 --> 1:05:02.942
-Omid, I need your help.

1:05:02.942 --> 1:05:04.770
-Yeah, what?

1:05:04.770 --> 1:05:07.642
-When we get to port, help me
keep everyone on the boat.

1:05:07.642 --> 1:05:09.644
-That'll never happen.

1:05:09.644 --> 1:05:12.299
First sniff of land, we'll
all be off and gone.

1:05:12.299 --> 1:05:15.302
-Just until we know
we're not infected!

1:05:15.302 --> 1:05:17.217
-Have you seen Sudi?

1:05:17.217 --> 1:05:18.392
Have you seen him?

1:05:18.392 --> 1:05:21.134
He needs help now.

1:05:21.134 --> 1:05:22.788
-Where do you live?

1:05:24.311 --> 1:05:25.704
Galway.

1:05:25.704 --> 1:05:27.401
-200,000 people
in Galway, right?

1:05:27.401 --> 1:05:29.099
-Yeah, it's about that.
-Yeah. We can't say

1:05:29.099 --> 1:05:30.970
we're so important that it's
worth risking the lives

1:05:30.970 --> 1:05:32.885
of 200,000 people.

1:05:32.885 --> 1:05:34.669
-Yeah, maybe.

1:05:34.669 --> 1:05:37.281
But who are you to say that
this poor kid has to die

1:05:37.281 --> 1:05:39.500
so someone else
can avoid the risk?

1:06:04.308 --> 1:06:09.269
-Are my eyes open or closed?

1:06:09.269 --> 1:06:11.184
-Open.

1:06:21.412 --> 1:06:23.892
Shh, you'll be alright.

1:06:23.892 --> 1:06:27.157
Shhhh.

1:06:27.157 --> 1:06:31.509
You'll be alright.

1:06:45.131 --> 1:06:47.003
Sudi?

1:07:27.043 --> 1:07:30.046
-God is our hope and strength.

1:07:30.046 --> 1:07:32.483
God is our hope.

1:07:32.483 --> 1:07:34.267
We will not fear,

1:07:34.267 --> 1:07:37.401
though we be in
the midst of the sea,

1:07:52.111 --> 1:07:58.074
-God is with us,
and we will not be removed.

1:07:58.074 --> 1:08:01.947
Amen.

1:08:21.793 --> 1:08:23.534
-We need to quarantine
ourselves now.

1:08:23.534 --> 1:08:26.014
-Maybe you've no life,
but we have responsibilities.

1:08:26.014 --> 1:08:29.627
-Listen.
Omid's wife is pregnant.

1:08:29.627 --> 1:08:31.324
We need to get them home.

1:08:31.324 --> 1:08:32.978
-If they want, they can
get themselves to hospital.

1:08:32.978 --> 1:08:35.546
Now seriously, fuck off!
-But you don't understand!

1:08:35.546 --> 1:08:37.374
-Did you not hear me?!

1:08:37.374 --> 1:08:39.332
Huh?!

1:09:09.884 --> 1:09:11.799
-You okay?

1:09:43.135 --> 1:09:45.398
How's Ger?

1:09:45.398 --> 1:09:48.836
-Not infected if that's
what you mean.

1:10:02.937 --> 1:10:05.897
-Aw, no.
Oh, no, no, no!

1:10:15.080 --> 1:10:18.214
Fucking...Fuck...
Come here.

1:10:29.268 --> 1:10:31.575
-Why has the engine stopped?

1:10:31.575 --> 1:10:33.011
-Tell them.

1:10:33.011 --> 1:10:36.144
-I disabled the boat.

1:10:36.144 --> 1:10:38.669
-What?

1:10:38.669 --> 1:10:40.584
-I disabled the boat.

1:10:40.584 --> 1:10:42.890
-Agh!
-Hey! Hey, hey, hey!

1:10:42.890 --> 1:10:45.415
-What the fuck's your problem?!

1:10:45.415 --> 1:10:48.026
-We've all got cuts.
-But we killed the eggs!

1:10:48.026 --> 1:10:49.897
-We could have got infected
before that!

1:10:49.897 --> 1:10:52.900
-So we get help!
-There is no help!

1:11:01.344 --> 1:11:03.433
-So...

1:11:03.433 --> 1:11:06.044
You want us to sit
out here and die?

1:11:06.044 --> 1:11:08.829
