-It's not mine.

1:11:14.052 --> 1:11:19.449
It's your family's.

1:11:19.449 --> 1:11:22.887
It's your husband's,
it's your baby's.

1:11:22.887 --> 1:11:24.758
Blame me if you want.

1:11:24.758 --> 1:11:26.760
We have to take action.

1:11:26.760 --> 1:11:29.807
We have to take responsibility.

1:11:55.049 --> 1:11:58.923
-Listen,
I know I caused this.

1:12:00.751 --> 1:12:02.361
-Don't.

1:12:07.279 --> 1:12:10.630
