-Mm-hmm.

1:13:01.638 --> 1:13:04.554
-I don't see anything.
-Look again. It's really faint.

1:13:14.259 --> 1:13:15.608
-No, I don't see anything.

1:13:15.608 --> 1:13:18.568
-Do me.

1:13:18.568 --> 1:13:20.700
-Not you. Omid.

1:13:20.700 --> 1:13:22.963
-Come on. Just let her do it.

1:13:38.152 --> 1:13:39.806
-I think you're fine.

1:13:39.806 --> 1:13:42.026
-Okay. My turn.

1:13:50.991 --> 1:13:53.080
-I don't see anything.

1:13:53.080 --> 1:13:56.606
-Okay.
-She scuppered us for nothing.

1:13:56.606 --> 1:13:59.391
-You haven't done me.

1:13:59.391 --> 1:14:02.960
-I don't need to do you.

1:14:02.960 --> 1:14:06.093
-What?

1:14:06.093 --> 1:14:07.965
-Give me that thing.

1:14:33.512 --> 1:14:35.253
-Fuck!

1:14:35.253 --> 1:14:37.081
Oh, God, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
-It's alright, it's okay.

1:14:37.081 --> 1:14:39.562
It's okay, it's alright.

1:14:39.562 --> 1:14:44.784
