tell anyone.

1:14:54.707 --> 1:14:57.101
I took us into
an exclusion zone.

1:14:57.101 --> 1:14:59.886
-That's why we saw the whales.

1:14:59.886 --> 1:15:01.714
-Come on.

1:15:01.714 --> 1:15:03.803
-You changed course?
-I changed course.

1:15:03.803 --> 1:15:06.284
