1:15:12.943 --> 1:15:14.814
Hmm?

1:15:14.814 --> 1:15:17.469
-Ger, come on.
-Ciara...

1:15:17.469 --> 1:15:20.733
-I think you should go.
-Come on.

1:15:20.733 --> 1:15:23.344
-You fucking bastard!
-Stop it!

1:15:23.344 --> 1:15:25.259
-Johnny's dead!
